36 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
37 the members of this body honor Mary Kay Murphy for her lifetime commitment to education
38 and community service as well as extend the most sincere best wishes for continued health
39 and happiness.
40 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
41 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to Mary
42 Kay Murphy.
